    <subfield code="a">• The state observer RAPTOR predicts tokamak plasma profile evolution in real-time. • The integration of the state observer RAPTOR in MARTe on RFX-mod is presented. • The validation of the state observer RAPTOR on RFX-mod q(a) &lt;2 plasmas is discussed.</subfield>
